.Dd February 17, 2017
.Dt MTC 4 vax
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm mtc
.Nd
.Tn UNIBUS
MSCP tape controller driver
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "mtc0 at uba? csr 0174500"
.Cd "mscpbus* at mtc?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver is for UNIBUS
tape controllers that use MSCP.
Among these controllers are:
.Bl -bullet -offset indent -compact
.It
DEC KLESI-U UNIBUS ctlr
.It
DEC TK50 Q22 bus ctlr
.El
The
.Nm
communicates with the host through
a packet protocol known as the Mass Storage Control Protocol
.Pq Tn MSCP .
Consult the file
.In mscp/mscp.h
for a detailed description of this protocol.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr vax/intro 4
.\".Xr ra 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver appeared in
.Nx 1.2 .
